				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The cost and the scaling needs to be examined. A purely AA-based solution is inappropriate as pets need to be able to mitigate appropriately for mages in their [Edit: late] 50s and 60s with limited AAs against the mobs they encounter as well. The base pets <span style="font-style: italic">do </span>need upgrades as well.
<br />

<br />
Remember also that Mages are in the situation of needing to spend AAs on themselves as well as their pets. As a result, direct comparison of pet-ability costs with melee costs is inappropriate.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Itchyban of Veeshan</a></span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by itchyban on Mon Feb 02, 2004 7:55 pm; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
