<br />
WAR&nbsp; 2271&nbsp; 15%&nbsp; 0&nbsp; &nbsp; 87&nbsp; &nbsp;21&nbsp; &nbsp; 223.3&nbsp; 71.1&nbsp; 2573&nbsp; 48.9&nbsp; 42.2&nbsp; NA&nbsp; &nbsp;4.2&nbsp; 5.9&nbsp; 5.3&nbsp; | 109.2
